{"title":"遥远的枪声","authors":["赵玉亮"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥远的枪声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵玉亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那两万五千里枪声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射程好远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今还在历史的深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隆隆轰鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令过来的人翻开往事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令后来的人陷入沉思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看铁与火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是以怎样的力度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切开层层黑暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交织出血色黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊心动魄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的每一声回音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在我们新的视野里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗成警钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织满蓝天的鸽哨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然把烽火和硝烟遥遥推成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开满大地的鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然把恐怖和苦难轻轻抹成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我们灵魂的上空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远闪耀着那颗美丽的红星"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}